{
  "id": "6a162c3ed42b53734b518373",
  "title": "中強度紛争のアセットギャップ",
  "created": 1779838015,
  "updated": 1779838114,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a162c3ed42b53734b518373",
      "text": "中強度紛争のアセットギャップ",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838015,
      "updated": 1779838015
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c3b0000000000065685",
      "text": "[tokoroten.icon]のClaudeの会話ログから自動生成された記事",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838016,
      "updated": 1779838024
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c430000000000065687",
      "text": "----",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838024,
      "updated": 1779838026
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c62000000000006568a",
      "text": "2026年イラン戦争の F-15 撃墜・ミサイル枯渇報道を題材に、自分が会話の中で組み立てた一行要約。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c62000000000006568b",
      "text": "「[* ドローン主体の中強度紛争に対して、適切なアセットを米軍は持っていなかった]」。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c62000000000006568c",
      "text": "これに対し AI から「アセット構成が両極端に偏っていた問題」という補強を得て、視座が固まった。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c62000000000006568d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c62000000000006568e",
      "text": "[*** 米軍のアセット構成は「両極端」]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c62000000000006568f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c620000000000065690",
      "text": "\t[* 高強度想定 (対中・対露)]: 高額精密兵器 (トマホーク、PrSM、THAAD)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c620000000000065691",
      "text": "\t[* 低強度想定 (対テロ)]: リーパー、A-10 のような安価装備",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c620000000000065692",
      "text": "\t[* 中強度の空白]: イランのように、大量の安価ドローン + 残存防空網を組み合わせる地域大国",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c620000000000065693",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c620000000000065694",
      "text": "→ 「コスト効率よく継戦できるレイヤー」が薄い。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c620000000000065695",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c620000000000065696",
      "text": "[*** 何が欠けていたか (構造的二択への追い込まれ方)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c620000000000065697",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c620000000000065698",
      "text": "table:table17",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c620000000000065699",
      "text": " 不足\t結果として強いられた選択",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c62000000000006569a",
      "text": " 安価ドローンの[* 安価な迎撃手段]\tパトリオット 8 発 / ドローン 1 機 のコスト非対称",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c62000000000006569b",
      "text": " 敵防空圏内で[* 使い捨て可能な攻撃用無人機の大量運用能力]\t高額ミサイル浪費 or 有人機投入 (F-15E 撃墜)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c62000000000006569c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c62000000000006569d",
      "text": "ウクライナ戦争が「ドローンと消耗戦の時代」を示していたのに、[* 中間領域への適応が追いついていない]。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c62000000000006569e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c62000000000006569f",
      "text": "[*** 第六世代戦闘機 (CCA) では埋まらない]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656a0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656a1",
      "text": "仮説: CCA / [スウォーム戦術]は「攻撃任務のリスク移転」だけで、コスト非対称問題は解かない。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838114
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656a2",
      "text": "1 機 2,500〜3,000 万ドルの CCA はシャヘド型ドローン (数万〜数百万円) の迎撃には高すぎる。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656a3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656a4",
      "text": "必要なのは三層:",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656a5",
      "text": "1. CCA / スウォーム — 有人機のリスク移転",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656a6",
      "text": "2. 低コスト迎撃 (レーザー、マイクロ波、安価インターセプター) — 飽和ドローン対処",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656a7",
      "text": "3. 米軍側が[* 使い捨て可能な安価攻撃ドローンを大量運用する]層",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656a9",
      "text": "第六世代は 1 のみ。2 と 3 は実戦配備できていない。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656ab",
      "text": "[*** なぜこの整理が効くか]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656ad",
      "text": "「F-15 撃墜の是非」「ミサイル枯渇」「CCA 投資判断」など個別論点が散在していたが、",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656ae",
      "text": "[* 中強度というレイヤーの空白]を中心軸に置くと、全部同じ問題の異なる断面と見える。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656af",
      "text": "[Anduril の本当の売り物は生産アーキテクチャ] への接続点でもある。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656b0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656b1",
      "text": "[*** 関連]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656b2",
      "text": "\t[Anduril の本当の売り物は生産アーキテクチャ]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656b3",
      "text": "\t[ウクライナ式分散ドローン製造の水平スケーリング]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c6200000000000656b4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838056,
      "updated": 1779838056
    },
    {
      "id": "6a162c3b0000000000065686",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779838016,
      "updated": 1779838016
    }
  ]
}